snippet.title: Scrap Age: Survivors
snippet.description:
*Update* 
Scrap Age Survivors is now live on the google play store! Follow the link below to play now!
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.FractalBlueEnt.ScrapAgeSurvivors&hl=en_US&gl=US

WE HAVE A BIG ANNOUNCEMENT!

Take a sneak peek at Scrap Age: Survivors!!!
Coming soon to most devices!

We are having a blast developing this new game and cannot wait to share more with everyone.

Follow our socials to stay up to date on the latest news!
